headline: Cboe Announces Derivatives and Data Vantage Leadership Appointments
summary: Cboe Global Markets, Inc. (Cboe: CBOE), the world's leading derivatives and securities exchange network, today announced the appointment of two industry veterans to lead its Derivatives and Data businesses. Rob Hocking rejoins as Executive Vice President, Global Head of Derivatives, and Brian McElligott joins as Senior Vice President, Global Head of Cboe Data Vantage. Hocking will succeed Cathy Clay who is departing the company for a new opportunity.
